1
00:00:11,632 --> 00:00:16,035
<i>Hey boys, listen up!</i>

2
00:00:16,103 --> 00:00:20,631
<i>Humans aren't such a big deal</i>

3
00:00:21,342 --> 00:00:25,472
<i>Who needs tomorrow anyway,</i>

4
00:00:25,546 --> 00:00:28,743
<i>so don't hide your fists</i>

5
00:00:30,685 --> 00:00:32,949
<i>You're not old enough</i>

6
00:00:33,020 --> 00:00:39,323
<i>to sell your dreams away to uncertainty</i>

7
00:00:40,261 --> 00:00:44,698
<i>Hey boys, you're the only ones</i>

8
00:00:44,765 --> 00:00:48,292
<i>who can pull the trigger in your heart</i>

9
00:00:49,737 --> 00:00:51,671
<i>All the kids said</i>

10
00:00:51,739 --> 00:00:54,674
<i>We're living in this senseless, ridiculous,</i>

11
00:00:54,742 --> 00:00:59,042
<i>awesome world right at this moment,</i>

12
00:00:59,246 --> 00:01:01,510
<i>All the kids said</i>

13
00:01:01,582 --> 00:01:07,384
<i>Don't forget every truth or lie</i>

14
00:01:08,789 --> 00:01:11,125
<i>All the kids said</i>

15
00:01:11,125 --> 00:01:13,457
<i>We're way too young to die</i>

16
00:01:13,527 --> 00:01:18,328
<i>In this empty town lined with empty faces</i>

17
00:01:18,399 --> 00:01:20,594
<i>All the kids took off</i>

18
00:01:20,668 --> 00:01:23,136
<i>into this windless night</i>

19
00:01:23,204 --> 00:01:26,571
<i>Because they want to change something</i>

20
00:01:31,456 --> 00:01:35,654
<i>Plea from a Friend</i>

21
00:01:51,409 --> 00:01:53,070
<i>That's Naruto?</i>

22
00:01:54,279 --> 00:01:55,940
<i>What is this intimidating power?</i>

23
00:01:56,915 --> 00:01:59,907
<i>And what was that</i>
<i>red Chakra earlier on?</i>

24
00:02:00,919 --> 00:02:02,819
<i>Is this guy a monster?</i>

25
00:02:05,890 --> 00:02:08,381
What the heck are you?!

26
00:02:09,661 --> 00:02:11,128
Your friend!

27
00:02:12,564 --> 00:02:14,327
That's why I'm telling you

28
00:02:14,399 --> 00:02:16,959
I'm not gonna let the likes
of Orochimaru get you!

29
00:02:17,135 --> 00:02:20,070
I'm telling you that I'll stop you...

30
00:02:20,138 --> 00:02:22,800
even if it means breaking
every bone in your arm and legs!

31
00:03:09,621 --> 00:03:12,055
<i>Fire Style.</i>
<i>Fire Ball Jutsu!</i>

32
00:03:55,333 --> 00:03:58,962
Come on! Wake up, already!

33
00:04:01,105 --> 00:04:04,905
If you don't come to your senses,
I'll have to break your bones

34
00:04:04,976 --> 00:04:08,434
so that you can't move
and I'll take you home that way, Sasuke!

35
00:04:16,454 --> 00:04:18,422
Shut up...

36
00:04:20,758 --> 00:04:23,488
What the heck do you,

37
00:04:23,561 --> 00:04:26,223
who has neither parents nor brothers,
think you understand?

38
00:04:27,532 --> 00:04:30,433
What makes you think that you,
who's been all alone from the start,

39
00:04:30,501 --> 00:04:32,628
can understand anything about me?!

40
00:04:36,541 --> 00:04:38,975
It's because I have the ties
that I feel this agony.

41
00:04:39,510 --> 00:04:42,070
How could you possibly understand...

42
00:04:42,146 --> 00:04:44,706
what it feels like to lose all that!

43
00:05:11,876 --> 00:05:15,107
It's true that I can't understand...

44
00:05:15,179 --> 00:05:17,545
how it feels to really
have parents or brothers...

45
00:05:18,883 --> 00:05:19,975
However...

46
00:05:20,151 --> 00:05:22,881
It's my treat today...
Eat your fill!

47
00:05:22,954 --> 00:05:24,717
Yippee!

48
00:05:24,989 --> 00:05:29,722
When I'm with Iruka Sensei,
I imagine...

49
00:05:29,827 --> 00:05:31,522
- Dig in!
- Dig in!

50
00:05:32,664 --> 00:05:35,531
Ninja, first of all, need to
warm their inner man.

51
00:05:37,835 --> 00:05:41,100
Hey! Hey! Don't get too carried away
and overeat!

52
00:05:42,707 --> 00:05:46,939
If this is...
what it feels like to have a dad.

53
00:05:49,447 --> 00:05:51,244
When I'm with you...

54
00:05:51,950 --> 00:05:54,282
Idiot, idiot, idiot...

55
00:05:54,519 --> 00:05:56,544
What was that, you loser?!

56
00:05:57,755 --> 00:06:00,690
I'm not gonna lose to you,
no matter what!

57
00:06:00,858 --> 00:06:02,325
Go ahead and say
whatever you want.

58
00:06:03,828 --> 00:06:05,056
How about this?

59
00:06:05,129 --> 00:06:07,097
Better not start feeling
too comfortable.

60
00:06:08,967 --> 00:06:12,664
I wonder... if having a brother
feels something like that.

61
00:06:14,806 --> 00:06:16,706
Why is it, Naruto...?

62
00:06:17,809 --> 00:06:20,471
Why is it that you go to
this extent for me?

63
00:06:20,812 --> 00:06:24,304
For me it's a tie that
I've finally been able to have!

64
00:06:45,203 --> 00:06:49,264
That's why I'm gonna stop you.

65
00:06:57,181 --> 00:07:03,120
It's too late, Naruto...
It's already too late.

66
00:07:05,723 --> 00:07:07,782
I can't go back anymore.

67
00:07:22,573 --> 00:07:23,904
Come, Naruto!

68
00:07:24,976 --> 00:07:28,377
In that case,
I just have to cut that tie.

69
00:07:35,086 --> 00:07:36,678
Cut, huh?

70
00:07:39,724 --> 00:07:43,091
Then why wear that headband now?

71
00:07:44,295 --> 00:07:47,890
I'll acknowledge you...
You're strong.

72
00:07:48,666 --> 00:07:50,065
And the reason for that is

73
00:07:50,134 --> 00:07:52,967
you're someone who knows
the pain of solitude as I do.

74
00:07:53,971 --> 00:07:57,429
And that pain makes people stronger.

75
00:07:58,109 --> 00:08:01,101
And for that very reason,
by cutting that tie,

76
00:08:01,179 --> 00:08:03,875
I will be able to obtain
even greater strength.

77
00:08:04,916 --> 00:08:09,080
I will fight you now on equal terms.
However...

78
00:08:09,987 --> 00:08:14,321
You won't even be able to
inflict a scratch on my forehead.

79
00:08:15,326 --> 00:08:17,556
That's something that
won't change in the least.

80
00:08:21,099 --> 00:08:24,762
It seems that whatever I say
won't have any effect anymore, huh?

81
00:08:26,137 --> 00:08:27,764
Sasuke!

82
00:08:28,372 --> 00:08:30,203
I'm done with talking...

83
00:08:31,142 --> 00:08:33,576
From here on, it's only fighting.

84
00:08:34,412 --> 00:08:35,436
Come!

85
00:08:47,892 --> 00:08:49,120
<i>I'm able to see...</i>

86
00:09:08,146 --> 00:09:10,080
<i>I'm now able to see</i>
<i>this guy's movements...</i>

87
00:09:10,148 --> 00:09:12,275
<i>which I wasn't able to see before.</i>

88
00:09:14,919 --> 00:09:16,079
<i>I'm able to see them!</i>

89
00:09:26,164 --> 00:09:29,691
<i>Sasuke's moving completely</i>
<i>different from a few moments ago.</i>

90
00:09:33,271 --> 00:09:35,569
<i>But I couldn't care less!</i>

91
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:39,599
<i>In any case, I can't afford to lose!</i>

92
00:09:40,011 --> 00:09:41,103
Damn it!

93
00:09:44,348 --> 00:09:47,647
<i>It must be the influence of my body</i>
<i>getting used to the state of Curse Mark.</i>

94
00:09:49,687 --> 00:09:51,154
<i>When he moves...</i>

95
00:09:51,222 --> 00:09:54,282
<i>by the subtle movements in</i>
<i>the way he exerts his strength...</i>

96
00:09:54,358 --> 00:09:58,590
<i>I can vividly see</i>
<i>an image of his next move.</i>

97
00:10:07,738 --> 00:10:09,467
<i>With my level of "eyes,"</i>

98
00:10:09,540 --> 00:10:12,407
<i>I don't need to use unnecessary Chakra</i>
<i>and can instead preserve it.</i>

99
00:10:13,644 --> 00:10:16,545
<i>The Curse Mark takes</i>
<i>too much Chakra.</i>

100
00:10:18,449 --> 00:10:20,110
<i>If I can see this much...</i>

101
00:10:20,184 --> 00:10:26,851
<i>I can time my attacks to the images of</i>
<i>Naruto's movements as I foresee them.</i>

102
00:10:44,575 --> 00:10:45,701
<i>This is no good...</i>

103
00:10:46,344 --> 00:10:48,938
<i>He's totally reading my movements.</i>

104
00:10:51,582 --> 00:10:53,345
<i>Damn it!</i>

105
00:11:07,163 --> 00:11:08,926
Oh, there you are.

106
00:11:09,766 --> 00:11:11,495
There's no mistake it's this way, right?

107
00:11:12,168 --> 00:11:13,260
Right.

108
00:11:14,303 --> 00:11:18,399
We better hurry.
I have a bad premonition.

109
00:12:13,830 --> 00:12:15,821
Sasuke!

110
00:12:25,942 --> 00:12:27,910
<i>Fire Style.</i>
<i>Dragon Flame Jutsu!</i>

111
00:13:17,260 --> 00:13:21,128
Sa su ke...

112
00:13:23,533 --> 00:13:25,524
It's too late, Naruto.

113
00:13:27,036 --> 00:13:30,870
It's too late now! Naruto!

114
00:14:40,176 --> 00:14:43,145
You're weak, aren't you, kid?

115
00:14:50,319 --> 00:14:54,756
You better be grateful to me...

116
00:14:55,825 --> 00:14:58,157
and to the Fourth Hokage

117
00:14:58,227 --> 00:15:02,857
who contained me within
the likes of you!

118
00:15:32,461 --> 00:15:34,599
What's going on?

119
00:16:50,439 --> 00:16:52,168
<i>What was that just now?</i>

120
00:16:52,975 --> 00:16:54,875
<i>Even if I'm able to read</i>
<i>Naruto's movements completely...</i>

121
00:16:54,944 --> 00:16:57,606
<i>his Chakra makes</i>
<i>a separate move of its own.</i>

122
00:16:59,015 --> 00:17:02,781
<i>It seems like the Chakra itself is moving</i>
<i>in accordance with its own will...</i>

123
00:17:04,687 --> 00:17:06,951
<i>Even with my "eyes"</i>
<i>I'm unable to read it completely.</i>

124
00:17:08,424 --> 00:17:11,655
<i>That red Chakra...</i>
<i>that's not an ordinary Chakra!</i>

125
00:17:14,630 --> 00:17:16,996
<i>Your target is Naruto, after all.</i>

126
00:17:17,266 --> 00:17:20,633
<i>To abduct Naruto</i>
<i>is the No. 1 priority</i>

127
00:17:20,703 --> 00:17:24,969
<i>placed by our organization, Akatsuki!</i>

128
00:17:25,741 --> 00:17:26,799
<i>I see...</i>

129
00:17:26,876 --> 00:17:30,403
<i>It appears that you have</i>
<i>some kind of special power.</i>

130
00:17:31,781 --> 00:17:33,408
Now I understand!

131
00:17:45,294 --> 00:17:47,489
<i>Fire Style.</i>
<i>Fire Ball Jutsu!</i>

132
00:18:05,948 --> 00:18:07,939
<i>That Chakra is protecting him?!</i>

133
00:18:11,954 --> 00:18:13,046
<i>Calm down.</i>

134
00:18:13,923 --> 00:18:17,290
<i>I won't be caught as long as</i>
<i>I fight from distance.</i>

135
00:19:13,816 --> 00:19:16,944
<i>Damn it... This is incredible!</i>

136
00:19:18,621 --> 00:19:20,452
<i>All I can do is dodge...</i>

137
00:19:50,753 --> 00:19:52,186
<i>Please let me get there in time.</i>

138
00:20:07,102 --> 00:20:10,196
Damn it, gimme a break...

139
00:20:11,807 --> 00:20:14,708
If I get tainted by this power...

140
00:20:14,777 --> 00:20:19,305
I don't even know what
will happen to me in the end...

141
00:20:20,616 --> 00:20:24,416
But, it can't be helped,
can it, Naruto?

142
00:20:37,233 --> 00:20:40,532
It is certainly true
that you were special...

143
00:20:42,705 --> 00:20:43,933
However...

144
00:20:45,140 --> 00:20:48,007
I am even more special than you.

145
00:20:55,684 --> 00:20:57,208
<i>Sasuke!</i>

146
00:21:12,232 --> 00:21:16,896
<i>When I recalled the parts one by one,</i>

147
00:21:16,970 --> 00:21:23,273
<i>I felt as though</i>
<i>I had understood everything</i>

148
00:21:23,343 --> 00:21:33,844
<i>Faded words which I kept so close to me</i>

149
00:21:34,154 --> 00:21:43,620
<i>Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,</i>

150
00:21:45,365 --> 00:21:50,359
<i>and this distant yearning for you</i>

151
00:21:50,670 --> 00:21:59,669
<i>I live, simply repeating this cycle</i>

152
00:22:01,848 --> 00:22:11,382
<i>Held in my two hands</i>
<i>A droplet of time</i>

153
00:22:12,826 --> 00:22:21,825
<i>Softly clutching forgotten memories</i>
<i>Lost words</i>

154
00:22:30,710 --> 00:22:34,578
<i>I'll keep these thoughts...</i>

155
00:22:37,383 --> 00:22:40,682
Damn! My body hurts!

156
00:22:41,120 --> 00:22:42,644
And to make it worse,

157
00:22:42,722 --> 00:22:45,782
I've completely lost feeling
in my left arm!

158
00:22:46,793 --> 00:22:49,057
Apparently this power
isn't something that

159
00:22:49,128 --> 00:22:52,359
I can just keep on using continuously!

160
00:22:53,499 --> 00:22:57,902
But... I can't give up!

161
00:22:58,304 --> 00:23:01,296
My next blow is
going to be the end!

162
00:23:02,141 --> 00:23:04,371
Next episode: "The End of Tears"
